'''Nintendo 3DS''' is an upcoming [[handheld game console]] developed by [[Nintendo]] and expected to be released in March 2011. The system is expected to be released at the [[Electronic Entertainment Expo]] in June 2010.<ref>http://ds.ign.com/articles/107/1079233p1.html</ref>

The 3DS will offer games that utilize 3D effects without the need for special glasses. The 3DS is also backwards compatible with Nintendo DS and DSi titles.

The system was announced on March 23, 2010 by Nintendo of Japan.<ref>http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2010/100323e.pdf</ref>

